name: Brushed Lemons
title: Brushed Lemons
description:
When life gives you lemons, make a cool shirt! Figure flattering and fresh, this crisp white shirt is overlaid with an artful watercolor-brushed lemon and speckled yellow pattern. Dress up this feminine fit with a skirt for Spring, or pair with jeans to keep it casual.

• Women's fit • 100% organic cotton • Fairtrade
